<header>
  <h1>Digitally Literate</h1>
  <p class="landing-subtitle">Weekly on digital literacy, AI, and education — {{ collections.newsletter | length }} issues since 2015.</p>
</header>

<p>Every week I send a short briefing on the forces shaping learning in the digital age — frameworks, insights, and tools for educators, researchers, and anyone paying attention to how technology changes how we read, write, and learn.</p>

<form
  action="https://buttondown.email/api/emails/embed-subscribe/digitallyliterate"
  method="post"
  target="popupwindow"
  onsubmit="window.open('https://buttondown.email/digitallyliterate', 'popupwindow')"
  class="newsletter-form"
>
  <label for="bd-email">Get next week's issue in your inbox:</label>
  <input type="email" name="email" id="bd-email" placeholder="Enter your email" required />
  <input type="submit" value="Subscribe" />
</form>

<hr>

<h2>Recent Issues</h2>

<div class="landing-list">
  {%- for note in collections.newsletter -%}
    {%- if loop.index <= 10 -%}
      <div class="landing-item">
        <a href="{{ note.url }}">{{ note.data.title or note.fileSlug }}</a>
        {%- if note.data.description %} — {{ note.data.description }}{% endif %}
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>

<hr>

<h2>Full Archive</h2>

<p><strong>Eras:</strong> TL;DR Foundation (issues 1–189, 2015–2018) · Digitally Literate (issues 190–300, 2019–2021) · Mature Analysis (issues 301–present, 2022–)</p>

<div class="book-filters">
  <input type="text" id="newsletter-filter" placeholder="Filter by title..." class="book-filter-input" autocomplete="off">
</div>

<div class="landing-list" id="newsletter-list">
  {%- for note in collections.newsletter -%}
    <div class="landing-item" data-title="{{ note.data.title | lower }}">
      <a href="{{ note.url }}">{{ note.data.title or note.fileSlug }}</a>
    </div>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>

<script>
(function() {
  var items = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('#newsletter-list .landing-item'));
  document.getElementById('newsletter-filter').addEventListener('input', function() {
    var q = this.value.toLowerCase();
    items.forEach(function(item) {
      item.style.display = item.dataset.title.indexOf(q) !== -1 ? '' : 'none';
    });
  });
})();
</script>
